                      <colophon xml:lang="am" xml:id="coloph1">
                        <locus from="49v" to="50r"/>
                        ተጽሐፈ፡ በመዋ<lb/>ዕለ፡ መንግሥቱ፡<lb/> ለዳግማዊ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7006Menilek">ምኒል<lb/>ክ፡</persName> ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡<lb/> ዘኢትዮጵያ፨ ወበ<lb/>መዋዕለ፡
                        ጵጵስናሁ<lb/><supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS4805Grebaut">፡</supplied> ለአባ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6876Matewos">ማቴዎስ፡</persName> ሊቀ፡<lb/>
                        ጳጳሳት፡ ዘኢትዮጵያ ወአጽሐፈ<supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS4805Grebaut">፡</supplied> <del rend="erasure"/>
                        ዘውእቱ፡ <supplied reason="omitted" resp="PRS4805Grebaut">ጸ</supplied>ሐፌ፡ ትእዛዝ፡ ወተጽሕፎቱሰ
                        <date calendar="grace" when="1899" when-custom="1891" evidence="internal">በ፲፰፻፺፩ ዓመተ፡ ምሕረት፡ ዘመን፡ ሉቃስ፡ ወርኅ፡ ነሓሴ</date>፨
                        <note>
                          The colophon states that the manuscript was written in the days of the reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7006Menilek">Mǝnilǝk II</persName> 
                          and during the episcopacy of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6876Matewos"><roleName type="office">ʾAbbā</roleName> Mātewos</persName>.
                          The colophon also states that the manuscript was written at the order of a ṣaḥāfe tǝʾzāz whose name was erased,
                          in the year of mercy <date calendar="ethiopian">1891 EC</date> in the era of Luke in the month of Naḥase.                       
                        </note>
                      </colophon>
